| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-2385 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 50b94709-591c-5809-834d-a4c5c7e9c5e1"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
